title: # 31 - Open Tabs
description:
Today on Open Tabs, I go through my internet search history for the week and talk about Red Dead Redemption 2, One star reviews, Frankensteins lab, Lucy Dacus, NPR’s top 10 albums of 2018, Freddy Soto and much more!
